Make sure to resolve paths to the realpath on Unixen.

the long term, this was actually a bug and this should make
symlinks work as expected on all Unix flavors.

Make sure to resolve paths to the realpath on Unixen.

In the short term, this should fix the errors on OSX.  In
the long term, this was actually a bug and this should make
symlinks work as expected on all Unix flavors.
